ft.<br /><br />Somewhere around here I have a larger version of that same picture, with the focus zoomed out.&nbsp; It's probably on one of my backup hard drives, but shows about a hundred basidia, and one can really see how the spores will go in all directions, not straight across or straight down.<br />RR<br /><br /><a href=\"https://files.shroomery.org/files/07-21/027681940-outdoorchulacopelandia1_w_credits_a.jpg\" class=\"highslide\" onclick=\"return hs.expand(this,{slideshowGroup:'hsg1'})\" target=\"_blank\"><img style=\"max-width:192px;height:auto;\" src=\"/forums/thumbs/07-21/027681940-thumb_outdoorchulacopelandia1_w_credits_a.jpg\"></a>","title":"Re: Embossed spore print? I need an explanation."}}